577
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:02,320
You might have to wait till dusk today.

578
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,720
I'll only do that for her.

579
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:06,090
I won't wait that long for anyone else.

580
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:07,400
Now that you've made money,

581
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,130
