582
00:22:11,050 --> 00:22:12,250
Let me treat you to...

583
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,180
Mending Meat Pies.

584
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,080
Sounds nice!

585
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:16,550
What do you think?

586
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:17,310
Do keep your word.

587
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:17,700
Sure.

588
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:20,910
Alright, talk to you later!

589
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:28,650
Look at you,

590
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,210
