604
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:51,240
Go do your things.

605
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:51,720
Bye!

606
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,000
Bye.

607
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,400
