622
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:37,680
She has become a superstar now.

623
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,590
You're so lucky.

624
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:38,980
Exactly.

625
00:23:38,980 --> 00:23:39,480
You must

626
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,590
