814
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:49,130
I learned something from the guys.

815
00:31:52,810 --> 00:31:59,420
Grow wild like spring grass.

816
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,940
I embrace the galaxy

817
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:03,900
in the gentle...

818
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:04,550
[Spring Grass]

819
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:07,640
In the gentle evening breeze.

820
00:32:08,050 --> 00:32:12,460
In the gentle evening breeze.

821
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:17,060
The sky slowly brightens into dawn.

822
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:19,740
Let me sing a song.

823
00:32:20,050 --> 00:32:22,960
Unyielding even in cracks,

824
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:25,510
wild grass thrives...

825
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:31,720
In the lushness of spring.

826
00:32:32,070 --> 00:32:37,350
In the lushness of spring.

827
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:40,610
It sounds nice.

828
00:32:42,310 --> 00:32:43,220
Sing it again.

829
00:32:43,830 --> 00:32:44,400
Okay.

830
00:32:47,350 --> 00:32:54,350
Grow wild like spring grass.

831
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:31,930
Let's have something foreign.

832
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:33,610
A bottle of vodka, please.

833
00:33:34,810 --> 00:33:35,720
