834
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,180
A bottle of vodka, please.

835
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:38,330
Okay, just a minute.

836
00:33:38,330 --> 00:33:39,380
Vodka.

837
00:33:39,530 --> 00:33:40,880
I'm speaking Russian
with a bit of an accent...

838
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:41,510
Jun.

839
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:42,250
Jun.

840
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:42,900
Jun.

841
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:44,050
Hurry, take a seat.

842
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:47,530
