860
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:21,080
Fine by me.

861
00:34:21,550 --> 00:34:22,350
-Sure.
-Okay.

862
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:24,900
Sir,

863
00:34:25,010 --> 00:34:25,800
the vodka you ordered.

864
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:26,340
We don't want it now.

865
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:26,960
Get us beers instead.

866
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,010
Three beers, please.

867
00:34:28,010 --> 00:34:28,820
How can we not drink vodka?

868
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:29,880
We'll take it. Thanks.

869
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:30,230
Okay.

870
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:30,710
Enjoy.

871
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:31,150
Thanks.

872
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:31,900
I-It is expensive.

873
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:32,630
For what it's worth,

874
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:33,960
today calls for a celebration.

875
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:35,489
We've made money after all.

876
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:37,510
Yes. Don't just focus on the losses.

877
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:39,000
We've got profits, right?

878
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,540
Right.

879
00:34:39,570 --> 00:34:41,199
I-I did have

880
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:43,050
a pretty good time on this trip.

881
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:46,960
I'll level with you.

882
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:50,320
We didn't make much money.

883
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,780
I went to the bank

884
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:53,960
and queued for over two hours.

885
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:55,760
This is all I got.

886
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:59,020
Only 300?

887
00:34:59,050 --> 00:35:00,550
M-My investment alone was 900.

888
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:02,080
Jun, are you joking with us?

889
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:14,860
I couldn't squeeze a tear.

890
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:19,090
I promised to help you guys make money.

891
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:21,500
But I failed—

892
00:35:22,730 --> 00:35:24,790
how was that possible?

893
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,300
Look what this is!

894
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:28,320
Gosh.

895
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:30,240
This is what we earned.

896
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:31,870
This is what we earned.

897
00:35:32,210 --> 00:35:33,740
This is also what we earned.

898
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,950
What is this?

899
00:35:35,150 --> 00:35:36,060
What is this?

900
00:35:36,130 --> 00:35:37,170
This much?

901
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,360
Of course!

902
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:40,110
Even brothers must
settle accounts clearly.

903
00:35:40,110 --> 00:35:41,500
Let's divide the money now.

904
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:43,740
Well, your investment was 3000 yuan.

905
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,380
So naturally,

906
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:46,480
you should receive

907
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:48,300
a total profit of 25,000, right?

908
00:35:48,570 --> 00:35:50,070
As for me, I paid for half of the cost.

909
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:51,200
This should be mine.

910
00:35:51,510 --> 00:35:54,160
And this... is what you earned.

911
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:56,780
But I think you deserve more.

912
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,110
I'll give you 3,000 extra.

913
00:35:58,110 --> 00:35:58,920
So you'll have 8,000 in total.

914
00:35:58,920 --> 00:35:59,920
What do you think?

915
00:36:00,010 --> 00:36:01,340
See, what did I tell you?

916
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:03,930
Good luck finds you
when you're with Lucky Ma!

917
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,440
I not only brought you back
safe and sound,

918
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,710
but also helped you rake in profits.

919
00:36:06,710 --> 00:36:09,240
Good luck finds you
when you're with Lucky Ma!

920
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,650
Come on, what are you waiting for?

921
00:36:10,650 --> 00:36:11,710
Dazed, aren't you?

922
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,920
Well, I only invested 900.

923
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:16,090
But I was given this much in return.

924
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:18,000
I-I shouldn't take the extra.

925
00:36:18,070 --> 00:36:19,400
They should split this.

926
00:36:19,460 --> 00:36:20,150
Okay.

927
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:20,820
Don't!

928
00:36:21,090 --> 00:36:23,150
If next time I invest more,

929
00:36:23,150 --> 00:36:24,320
I'll gain more, right?

930
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:24,840
Of course.

931
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:26,480
The more you invest, the more you gain.

932
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,610
Buy a car later.

933
00:36:27,690 --> 00:36:29,210
You invested little and earned little,

934
00:36:29,210 --> 00:36:30,820
I still gave you a higher total.

935
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:31,280
Come on.

936
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,210
Time for drinks, guys.

937
00:36:32,210 --> 00:36:33,190
-Drink up.
-To Mr. Lucky!

938
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:33,920
To Mr. Lucky!

939
00:36:33,940 --> 00:36:35,170
-Come on.
-Guys, chug it!

940
00:36:35,170 --> 00:36:35,670
Bottoms up!

941
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,110
Bottoms up!

942
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:36,840
Thanks, Jun!

943
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:42,730
[No photos] [No smoking]

944
00:36:40,110 --> 00:36:40,840
Mr. Yang.

945
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,200
Let's get in the room.

946
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,510
Are you the singer to record a song here?

947
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:50,960
Yes.

948
00:36:51,150 --> 00:36:52,230
She is Zhuang Zhuang, the singer

949
00:36:52,230 --> 00:36:53,160
I told you about.

950
00:36:53,650 --> 00:36:54,510
Zhuang Zhuang,

951
00:36:55,090 --> 00:36:55,800
I put some marks

952
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:56,570
and highlighted

953
00:36:56,570 --> 00:36:57,340
a few key points here.

954
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:58,000
Take a look.

955
00:36:58,030 --> 00:37:00,420
[No photos] [No smoking]

956
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:58,760
Sure.

957
00:36:59,190 --> 00:37:00,320
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

958
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:01,640
Here's the plan.

959
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:02,440
I'll go in

960
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:04,070
and adjust the equipment in a bit.

961
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:04,690
Then, I will

962
00:37:04,690 --> 00:37:06,360
get you in there to familiarize you
with the place.

963
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:07,730
Stay here and get ready for now,

964
00:37:07,730 --> 00:37:08,060
okay?

965
00:37:08,070 --> 00:37:08,880
Okay.

966
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:09,670
Sure.

967
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:30,590
Grow wild like spring grass.

968
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:38,480
I embrace the galaxy
in the gentle evening breeze.

969
00:37:39,010 --> 00:37:43,050
The sky slowly brightens into dawn.

970
00:37:43,170 --> 00:37:45,660
Let me sing a song.

971
00:37:46,090 --> 00:37:49,100
Unyielding even in cracks,

972
00:37:49,380 --> 00:37:58,230
wild grass thrives
in the lushness of spring.

973
00:38:06,010 --> 00:38:12,230
Grow wild like spring grass.

974
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:15,010
I embrace the galaxy in...

975
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,610
I'm asking you to sing.

976
00:38:17,610 --> 00:38:19,270
Pretend this is a microphone.

977
00:38:22,780 --> 00:38:25,030
It's fair to say a big task
has been completed.

978
00:38:25,030 --> 00:38:27,560
The effort in the past six months
has paid off.

979
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:29,120
Above all,

980
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:32,280
I need to thank you,
Mr. Xu the great screenwriter.

981
00:38:33,570 --> 00:38:35,510
In fact, when I first came to Beijing,

982
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:38,130
I was totally focused on
becoming a screenwriter.

983
00:38:38,130 --> 00:38:39,840
I even made a resolution

984
00:38:40,610 --> 00:38:41,630
that until I became

985
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:43,210
a real screenwriter,

986
00:38:43,340 --> 00:38:44,190
I would never consider

987
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:45,850
any romantic relationships.

988
00:38:46,150 --> 00:38:48,410
Have you ever read martial arts novels?

989
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,500
All the great heroes written in those

990
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:52,130
have to detach themselves
from worldly desires

991
00:38:52,130 --> 00:38:54,280
when they practice peerless martial arts.

992
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:55,730
That's roughly it.

993
00:38:56,210 --> 00:38:57,340
But I found...

994
00:38:58,730 --> 00:39:00,730
t-that the two of us...

995
00:39:04,530 --> 00:39:05,390
Zhuang Zhuang!

996
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:09,200
Zhuang Zhuang!

997
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:11,930
Zhuang Zhuang!

998
00:39:14,150 --> 00:39:15,010
Zhuang Zhuang!

999
00:39:17,150 --> 00:39:17,570
Zhuang Zhuang!

1000
00:39:17,570 --> 00:39:18,230
Xu Shengli!

1001
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:23,690
Zhuang Zhuang, why did you hop off?

1002
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:26,120
You didn't even notice I was left behind.

1003
00:39:40,570 --> 00:39:42,070
Are you backing out now?

1004
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,980
D-Did you hear what I said?

1005
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,210
What did you say?

1006
00:39:53,730 --> 00:39:54,860
You know what I said.

1007
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,960
What was it?

1008
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:04,110
Please be my girlfriend.

1009
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,970
Do you have to think about it that long?

1010
00:40:49,050 --> 00:40:49,910
Get on the bike.

1011
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:51,340
Okay.

1012
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,810
It's so much warmer this way.

1013
00:40:59,090 --> 00:41:00,950
Winter in Beijing is really long.

1014
00:41:02,210 --> 00:41:04,070
Spring is approaching, isn't it?

1015
00:41:05,730 --> 00:41:08,230
Actually, winter is also quite nice.

1016
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,420
I have already

1017
00:41:24,900 --> 00:41:26,980
transferred my energy to you.

1018
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:30,420
Next, I'll ask you questions

1019
00:41:30,730 --> 00:41:32,590
and you'll give me answers, okay?

1020
00:41:33,090 --> 00:41:33,670
Okay.

1021
00:41:36,210 --> 00:41:38,230
How many years have you been paralyzed?

1022
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:39,520
More than 20 years.

1023
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:41,500
Do you know why

1024
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,230
you could never stand up

1025
00:41:43,230 --> 00:41:44,560
during all these years?

1026
00:41:45,010 --> 00:41:45,920
No, I don't.

1027
00:41:47,460 --> 00:41:49,260
It's because you didn't meet me.

1028
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:52,480
If you had met me earlier,

1029
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:55,720
you would've been able
to stand up long ago.

1030
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:58,660
Suppose I help you

1031
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:01,510
stand up today,

1032
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,460
how will you repay me?

1033
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:08,460
However much money you want,

1034
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:10,090
I-I'll pay you!

1035
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,930
Money talk is too tacky.

1036
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:17,130
When I meet the right patient,

1037
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:20,800
I won't even charge a dime.

1038
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:24,920
If not, no amount of money
can buy my service.

1039
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:27,800
How kind.

1040
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,400
How very kind of you.

1041
00:42:31,170 --> 00:42:32,930
Is this how you talk to

1042
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:34,560
a great kind soul, so rudely?

1043
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:35,550
Stand up now.

1044
00:42:38,010 --> 00:42:38,870
Don't help him.

1045
00:42:42,050 --> 00:42:42,710
Honey...

1046
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,010
You've stood up, right?

1047
00:42:46,010 --> 00:42:47,870
Master, I can stand on my feet now.

1048
00:42:49,050 --> 00:42:50,210
Uncle, actually...

1049
00:42:51,500 --> 00:42:52,430
Speak your mind.

1050
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,230
I wonder if you could

1051
00:42:55,610 --> 00:42:56,120
let me

1052
00:42:56,230 --> 00:42:57,420
join your business.
